About
=====

Integration with `Hashicorp Consul <https://www.consul.io>`_.

Use
---

.. code-block:: yaml

    consul:
      host: localhost:8500  # optional
      service:              # optional
        name: my
        tags:
          - worker


Development
-----------

Check code:

.. code-block:: shell

    hatch run lint:all


Format code:

.. code-block:: shell

    hatch run lint:fmt


Run tests:

.. code-block:: shell

    hatch run pytest


Run tests with coverage:

.. code-block:: shell

    hatch run cov
